s=\"text-xs font-bold text-gray-400 uppercase mb-2\" data-kid=\"317\">Gold</span>\n                    <span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-[var(--dark-green)] mb-1 italic\" data-kid=\"318\">₹50,000</span>\n                    <button class=\"mt-4 w-full py-2.5 rounded-lg bg-[var(--accent-gold)] text-white font-bold text-sm shadow-md hover:bg-[#ae8231] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"319\">Select</button>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl card-shadow border border-gray-100 flex flex-col items-center text-center\" data-kid=\"320\">\n                    <span class=\"text-xs font-bold text-gray-400 uppercase mb-2\" data-kid=\"321\">Platinum</span>\n                    <span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-[var(--dark-green)] mb-1 italic\" data-kid=\"322\">₹75,000</span>\n                    <button class=\"mt-4 w-full py-2.5 rounded-lg border border-[var(--primary-green)] text-[var(--primary-green)] font-bold text-sm\" data-kid=\"323\">Select</button>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <a href=\"#\" class=\"text-[var(--primary-green)] font-bold flex items-center justify-center gap-2 hover:underline\" data-kid=\"324\">\n                View All Sponsorship Benefits <i class=\"ri-arrow-right-line\" data-kid=\"325\"></i>\n            </a>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  \n  <section class=\"py-20 bg-white\" data-kid=\"326\">\n    <div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6\" data-kid=\"327\">\n        <div class=\"flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-16 p-12 rounded-[40px] bg-[var(--cream-white)] border border-gray-100\" data-kid=\"328\">\n            <div class=\"lg:w-3/5\" data-kid=\"329\">\n                <div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-6\" data-kid=\"330\">\n                    <div class=\"w-10 h-10 bg-[var(--dark-green)] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white\" data-kid=\"331\">\n                        <i class=\"ri-global-line\" data-kid=\"332\"></i>\n                    </div>\n                    <h3 class=\"text-3xl font-serif text-[var(--dark-green)]\" data-kid=\"333\">Aligned with Global Goals</h3>\n                </div>\n                <p class=\"text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-10 text-lg\" data-kid=\"334\">We are committed to the UN Sustainable Development Goals and the vision of <strong class=\"text-[var(--primary-green)]\" data-kid=\"335\">Viksit Bharat @2047</strong>. Our platform actively drives impact for:</p>\n                <div class=\"grid grid-cols-4 md:grid-cols-8 gap-4\" data-kid=\"336\">\n                    <div class=\"group relative flex flex-col items-center\" data-kid=\"337\">\n                        <div class=\"w-14 h-14 bg-[#fcc30b] rounded flex items-center justify-center text-white font-black text-xl shadow-lg transition-transform group-hover:-translate-y-1\" data-kid=\"338\">7</div>\n                        <span class=\"absolute -bottom-8 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 text-[8px] font-bold uppercase whitespace-nowrap opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity\" data-kid=\"339\">Energy</span>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"group relative flex flex-col items-center\" data-kid=\"340\">\n                        <div class=\"w-14 h-14 bg-[#a21942] rounded flex items-center justify-center text-white font-black text-xl shadow-lg transition-transform group-hover:-translate-y-1\" data-kid=\"341\">8</div>\n                        <span class=\"absolute -bottom-8 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 text-[8px] font-bold uppercase whitespace-nowrap opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity\" data-kid=\"342\">Work</span>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"group relative flex flex-col items-center\" data-kid=\"343\">\n                        <div class=\"w-14 h-14 bg-[#fd6925] rounded flex items-center justify-center text-white font-black text-xl shadow-lg transition-transform group-hover:-translate-y-1\" data-kid=\"344\">9</div>\n                        <span class=\"absolute -bottom-8 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 text-[8px] font-bold uppercase whitespace-nowrap opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity\" data-kid=\"345\">Industry</span>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"group relative flex flex-col items-center\" data-kid=\"346\">\n                        <div class=\"w-14 h-14 bg-[#ff9d24] rounded flex items-center justify-center text-white font-black text-xl shadow-lg transition-transform group-hover:-translate-y-1\" data-kid=\"347\">11</div>\n                        <span class=\"absolute -bottom-8 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 text-[8px] font-bold uppercase whitespace-nowrap opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity\" data-kid=\"348\">Cities</span>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"group relative flex flex-col items-center\" data-kid=\"349\">\n                        <div class=\"w-14 h-14 bg-[#bf8b2e] rounded flex items-center justify-center text-white font-black text-xl shadow-lg transition-transform group-hover:-translate-y-1\" data-kid=\"350\">12</div>\n                        <span class=\"absolute -bottom-8 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 text-[8px] font-bold uppercase whitespace-nowrap opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity\" data-kid=\"351\">Impact</span>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"group relative flex flex-col items-center\" data-kid=\"352\">\n                        <div class=\"w-14 h-14 bg-[#3f7e44] rounded flex items-center justify-center text-white font-black text-xl shadow-lg transition-transform group-hover:-translate-y-1\" data-kid=\"353\">13</div>\n                        <span class=\"absolute -bottom-8 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 text-[8px] font-bold uppercase whitespace-nowrap opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity\" data-kid=\"354\">Climate</span>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"group relative flex flex-col items-center\" data-kid=\"355\">\n                        <div class=\"w-14 h-14 bg-[#56ad46] rounded flex items-center justify-center text-white font-black text-xl shadow-lg transition-transform group-hover:-translate-y-1\" data-kid=\"356\">15</div>\n                        <span class=\"absolute -bottom-8 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 text-[8px] font-bold uppercase whitespace-nowrap opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity\" data-kid=\"357\">Life</span>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"group relative flex flex-col items-center\" data-kid=\"358\">\n                        <div class=\"w-14 h-14 bg-[#19486a] rounded flex items-center justify-center text-white font-black text-xl shadow-lg transition-transform group-hover:-translate-y-1\" data-kid=\"359\">17</div>\n                        <span class=\"absolute -bottom-8 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 text-[8px] font-bold uppercase whitespace-nowrap opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity\" data-kid=\"360\">Partners</span>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"lg:w-1/3 text-center lg:text-right border-t lg:border-t-0 lg:border-l border-gray-200 pt-10 lg:pt-0 lg:pl-16\" data-kid=\"361\">\n                <p class=\"text-[var(--dark-green)] font-serif text-4xl lg:text-5xl italic mb-6 leading-tight\" data-kid=\"362\">आइए, साथ मिलकर एक बेहतर भविष्य का निर्माण करें।</p>\n                <p class=\"text-gray-500 text-sm italic font-medium\" data-kid=\"363\">\"Let us, together, build a better future.\"</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  \n  <footer class=\"bg-[var(--dark-green)] text-white pt-24 pb-12\" data-kid=\"364\">\n    <div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6\" data-kid=\"365\">\n      <div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-12 mb-20\" data-kid=\"366\">\n        \n        <div class=\"space-y-6\" data-kid=\"367\">\n          <div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\" data-kid=\"368\">\n            <div class=\"w-10 h-10 bg-[var(--primary-green)] rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-white\" data-kid=\"369\">\n              <i class=\"ri-leaf-fill text-2xl\" data-kid=\"370\"></i>\n            </div>\n            <span class=\"text-2xl font-serif font-bold tracking-tight\" data-kid=\"371\">GOLDEN PRENEUR</span>\n          </div>\n          <p class=\"text-white/60 leading-relaxed\" data-kid=\"372\">\n            India's most comprehensive green entrepreneurship platform. Empowering innovators redefining sustainability across the nation.\n          </p>\n          <div class=\"flex gap-4\" data-kid=\"373\">\n            <a href=\"#\" class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-white/5 flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-[var(--accent-gold)] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"374\"><i class=\"ri-instagram-line\" data-kid=\"375\"></i></a>\n            <a href=\"#\" class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-white/5 flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-[var(--accent-gold)] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"376\"><i class=\"ri-linkedin-fill\" data-kid=\"377\"></i></a>\n            <a href=\"#\" class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-white/5 flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-[var(--accent-gold)] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"378\"><i class=\"ri-facebook-fill\" data-kid=\"379\"></i></a>\n            <a href=\"#\" class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-white/5 flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-[var(--accent-gold)] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"380\"><i class=\"ri-youtube-fill\" data-kid=\"381\"></i></a>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        \n        \n        <div data-kid=\"382\">\n          <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold mb-8 text-[var(--accent-gold)] uppercase tracking-widest text-sm\" data-kid=\"383\">Quick Links</h4>\n          <ul class=\"space-y-4 text-white/60\" data-kid=\"384\">\n            <li data-kid=\"385\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\" data-kid=\"386\">About 1MEIF</a></li>\n            <li data-kid=\"387\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\" data-kid=\"388\">Award Categories</a></li>\n            <li data-kid=\"389\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\" data-kid=\"390\">Nomination Process</a></li>\n            <li data-kid=\"391\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\" data-kid=\"392\">Past Winners</a></li>\n            <li data-kid=\"393\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\" data-kid=\"394\">Venue & Directions</a></li>\n          </ul>\n        </div>\n        \n        \n        <div data-kid=\"395\">\n          <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold mb-8 text-[var(--accent-gold)] uppercase tracking-widest text-sm\" data-kid=\"396\">Participate</h4>\n          <ul class=\"space-y-4 text-white/60\" data-kid=\"397\">\n            <li data-kid=\"398\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\" data-kid=\"399\">Apply for Award</a></li>\n            <li data-kid=\"400\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\" data-kid=\"401\">Become a Sponsor</a></li>\n            <li data-kid=\"402\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\" data-kid=\"403\">Exhibition Stalls</a></li>\n            <li data-kid=\"404\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\" data-kid=\"405\">Speaker Application</a></li>\n            <li data-kid=\"406\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\" data-kid=\"407\">Get Delegate Pass</a></li>\n          </ul>\n        </div>\n        \n        \n        <div data-kid=\"408\">\n          <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold mb-8 text-[var(--accent-gold)] uppercase tracking-widest text-sm\" data-kid=\"409\">Contact Us</h4>\n          <ul class=\"space-y-4 text-white/60\" data-kid=\"410\">\n            <li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\" data-kid=\"411\">\n              <i class=\"ri-map-pin-line mt-1 text-[var(--accent-gold)]\" data-kid=\"412\"></i>\n              <span data-kid=\"413\">Ahmedabad, Gujarat, India</span>\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"flex items-center gap-3\" data-kid=\"414\">\n              <i class=\"ri-phone-line text-[var(--accent-gold)]\" data-kid=\"415\"></i>\n              <span data-kid=\"416\">+91 70411 51714</span>\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"flex items-center gap-3\" data-kid=\"417\">\n              <i class=\"ri-mail-line text-[var(--accent-gold)]\" data-kid=\"418\"></i>\n              <span data-kid=\"419\">hello@goldenpreneur.in</span>\n            </li>\n          </ul>\n          <button class=\"mt-8 bg-green-500 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-xl font-bold flex items-center gap-2 text-sm w-full justify-center\" data-kid=\"420\">\n            <i class=\"ri-whatsapp-line text-lg\" data-kid=\"421\"></i> WHATSAPP US\n          </button>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      \n      \n      <div class=\"pt-12 border-t border-white/5 flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-8 text-center lg:text-left relative\" data-kid=\"422\">\n        <div class=\"space-y-2 max-w-2xl\" data-kid=\"423\">\n            <p class=\"text-sm text-white/40\" data-kid=\"424\">© 2026 Golden preneur | Organised by 1 Million Entrepreneurs International Forum (1MEIF)</p>\n            <p class=\"text-[10px] text-white/20 uppercase tracking-[0.15em] leading-loose\" data-kid=\"425\">Section 8 NGO | NGO Darpan Certified | CSR No.: CSR00106194 | 80G & 12A | Viksit Bharat @2047 | CEED Association Partner</p>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"lg:absolute -top-16 right-0\" data-kid=\"426\">\n          <a href=\"https://wa.me/917041151714\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"w-14 h-14 bg-[#25D366] rounded-full shadow-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-white text-3xl hover:scale-110 transition-transform\" data-kid=\"427\">\n            <i class=\"ri-whatsapp-line\" data-kid=\"428\"></i>\n          </a>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-6\" data-kid=\"429\">\n          <a href=\"#\" class=\"text-xs text-white/40 hover:text-white\" data-kid=\"430\">Privacy Policy</a>\n          <a href=\"#\" class=\"text-xs text-white/40 hover:text-white\" data-kid=\"431\">Terms of Service</a>\n          <a href=\"#\" class=\"text-xs text-white/40 hover:text-white\" data-kid=\"432\">Refund Policy</a>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </footer>\n\n</div>\n",
