"57\">✓</span>\n                            <span class=\"text-gray-700\" data-kid=\"58\">Invitation-based or self-nomination</span>\n                        </li>\n                        <li class=\"flex items-center gap-3\" data-kid=\"59\">\n                            <span class=\"w-6 h-6 bg-[var(--color-primary)]/10 text-[var(--color-primary)] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sm\" data-kid=\"60\">✓</span>\n                            <span class=\"text-gray-700\" data-kid=\"61\">Recognition for long-term impact</span>\n                        </li>\n                        <li class=\"flex items-center gap-3\" data-kid=\"62\">\n                            <span class=\"w-6 h-6 bg-[var(--color-primary)]/10 text-[var(--color-primary)] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sm\" data-kid=\"63\">✓</span>\n                            <span class=\"text-gray-700\" data-kid=\"64\">Prestigious industry validation</span>\n                        </li>\n                    </ul>\n\n                    <button class=\"w-full bg-[var(--color-primary)] text-white py-5 rounded-2xl font-bold text-lg hover:bg-[var(--color-dark)] transition-all flex items-center justify-center gap-3 shadow-lg shadow-[var(--color-primary)]/20\" data-kid=\"65\">\n                        Apply for Honorary Track <svg class=\"w-6 h-6\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" data-kid=\"66\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3\" data-kid=\"67\"></path></svg>\n                    </button>\n                </div>\n\n                \n                <div class=\"bg-[var(--color-dark)] border-2 border-[var(--color-gold)] rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-12 shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-all relative overflow-hidden flex flex-col text-white\" data-kid=\"68\">\n                    <div class=\"absolute -bottom-8 -left-8 w-48 h-48 bg-[var(--color-gold)]/10 rounded-full\" data-kid=\"69\"></di