class=\"fas fa-envelope pt-1\" data-kid=\"280\"></i>\n                            <span data-kid=\"281\">hello@goldenpreneur.in</span>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-white/50\" data-kid=\"282\">\n                            <i class=\"fas fa-location-dot pt-1\" data-kid=\"283\"></i>\n                            <span data-kid=\"284\">Ahmedabad, Gujarat, India</span>\n                        </div>\n                        <a href=\"https://wa.me/917041151714\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 bg-[#25D366] text-white rounded-lg text-sm font-bold mt-4 hover:scale-105 transition-transform\" data-kid=\"285\">\n                            <i class=\"fab fa-whatsapp text-lg\" data-kid=\"286\"></i>\n                            Chat with us\n                        </a>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"pt-8 border-t border-white/10 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-6 text-xs text-white/40 uppercase tracking-widest\" data-kid=\"287\">\n                <div class=\"text-center md:text-left\" data-kid=\"288\">\n                    © 2026 GOLDEN PRENEUR | 1 MILLION ENTREPRENEURS INTERNATIONAL FORUM | SECTION 8 NGO | CEED PARTNER\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"flex gap-4\" data-kid=\"289\">\n                    <span data-kid=\"290\">CSR No.: CSR00106194</span>\n                    <span data-kid=\"291\">80G & 12A Certified</span>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"mt-8 text-center text-sm font-hindi opacity-60\" data-kid=\"292\">\n                आइए, साथ मिलकर एक बेहतर भविष्य का निर्माण करें।\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n</div>\n",
