 data-kid=\"382\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check-circle-2 text-[var(--leaf-green)]\" data-kid=\"383\"><path d=\"M12 22c5.523 0 10-4.477 10-10S17.523 2 12 2 2 6.477 2 12s4.477 10 10 10z\" data-kid=\"384\"></path><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\" data-kid=\"385\"></path></svg> 80G & 12A Certified</span>\n          <span class=\"flex items-center gap-2\" data-kid=\"386\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-users-2 text-[var(--primary-green)]\" data-kid=\"387\"><path d=\"M14 19a6 6 0 0 0-12 0\" data-kid=\"388\"></path><circle cx=\"8\" cy=\"9\" r=\"4\" data-kid=\"389\"></circle><path d=\"M22 19a6 6 0 0 0-6-6 4 4 0 1 0 0-8\" data-kid=\"390\"></path></svg> CEED Association Partner</span>\n          <span class=\"text-[var(--dark-green)] font-bold italic border-l pl-6 border-gray-200\" data-kid=\"391\">आइए, साथ मिलकर एक बेहतर भविष्य का निर्माण करें।</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </footer>\n\n</div>\n",
